{"tid":1879303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被護照上的China所害 旅客常要解釋半天才能登機","createTime":"2020-02-14T06:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T11:07:15.000Z","uid":144372,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"50a79d89fb33ffe796b30ac31ebdae7ef3e4f787","tid":1879303,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3066307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3066307&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKRxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=2fd55fa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3066307&h=9c378d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3066307</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/12/3066307_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F12%2F3066307_1_1.jpg&h=86549116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔記者林曉雲／台北報導〕護照上的「Republic of China」，讓台灣人民在出入境其他國家時，常被誤會為中國人，造成非常多的困擾。中興大學國際長陳牧民在臉書發文，指他在斯里蘭卡要搭機時，必須要先解釋「台灣和中國不同」，解釋半天才能順利登機，真的很「hate」這本護照。<br />\n<br />\n陳牧民接受本報記者訪問時表示，在旅程中經過的每個機場，他都要解釋很久才能登機，尤其是在中國武漢肺炎疫情發燒的此時更嚴重，要不斷的說明「台灣和中國不同」，才能順利搭機。<br />\n<br />\n臉友們在陳牧民的發文中紛紛留言，有臉友表示，當年2003年在護照上加「TAIWAN」，是克服不少阻擋的結果，現在如要改護照，應該會比較容易；也有臉友認為，應該只留TAIWAN；另有臉友主張改成Republic of TAIWAN。<br />\n<br />\n也有臉友舉自身經驗表示，在歐洲退稅時，店員就會指著他護照上的China，要求出示簽證，住飯店時也被要求出示簽證，每次都要說明一番；另也有臉友分享，曾在德國入境時被誤為中國人，海關告訴他「你是中國人，需要簽證。」後來是另名海關指著他護照上的蓋章說：「他的國家是TAIWAN，所以他不需要簽證。」才順利通關。"},{"pid":"0b65b5b141c496cafc890f29b542533f322f8fab","tid":1879303,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"關於派口罩，我支持剩係派畀手足，歡迎入嚟屌柒我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1879264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1879264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b482c6f0c3c1349eb42fbaf22ccabfc26d3ab40f","tid":1879303,"uid":78533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以台獨未成功?"},{"pid":"a0d57f41257fbcdfb83ec4cc1a91d4c41b3b458e","tid":1879303,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"係呢個時候講Taiwan is not China"},{"pid":"75eb28b270c09beba3acaaa6bebc01a8bdde9a22","tid":1879303,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"根本係一個好好契機改埋個名<br />\n唔改名就當你中国人"},{"pid":"0e334e5025bd4ccb6b595bb675f31c22249db17a","tid":1879303,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"印台灣Taiwan 咪算囉，冇混淆餘地"},{"pid":"d06f47b021717c874f0b5ef84904ec27f5d52cac","tid":1879303,"uid":159413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"班台仔想保住個名反攻中国<br />\n又要嫌煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff14bc45b8260c3d7267fb485b6050907e3360b","tid":1879303,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75eb28b270c09beba3acaaa6bebc01a8bdde9a22","tid":1879303,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"根本係一個好好契機改埋個名<br />\n唔改名就當你中国人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"Republic of China 根本外國人唔撚知你係乜<br />\n正如我喺連登Post堆非洲國家名連登都唔知邊個打邊個"},{"pid":"a1b7b217102c16d0a131e96ce702c382e8c78756","tid":1879303,"uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d06f47b021717c874f0b5ef84904ec27f5d52cac","tid":1879303,"uid":159413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"班台仔想保住個名反攻中国<br />\n又要嫌煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"邊個台仔要反攻中國?"},{"pid":"c06d2e58c35a84e9b315fbcbf62d91c902623906","tid":1879303,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc